33:10.292 --> 33:12.947
But there's one thing
you must do.

33:12.991 --> 33:14.993
Change its name.

33:15.036 --> 33:16.255
- What's wrong with Callie?

33:16.298 --> 33:18.909
- Kali is a sacred
Hindu goddess.

33:18.953 --> 33:21.782
