33:56.947 --> 33:59.298
It's okay.
You can say it.

33:59.341 --> 34:01.778
I did the best I could.

34:02.997 --> 34:05.260
- Yeah, you did.

34:05.304 --> 34:06.609
You see?

34:06.653 --> 34:08.089
The story itself
is less powerful

34:08.133 --> 34:10.135
than the way we tell it,
isn't it?

34:13.442 --> 34:15.096
I'm just...

34:17.664 --> 34:19.274
I'm really sorry.

34:19.318 --> 34:21.711
- For what?

34:21.755 --> 34:24.888
- For all us adults making you
kids deal with this problem

34:24.932 --> 34:26.847
rather than fixing it
ourselves.

34:26.890 --> 34:28.414
That's not fair.
- Yeah.

34:28.457 --> 34:31.765
We've received your
thoughts and prayers, thanks.

34:32.983 --> 34:35.116
- But you know
what gives me hope?

34:35.160 --> 34:37.162
- What?
- You.

34:37.205 --> 34:39.686
You and your whole generation.
You've blown me away.

34:39.729 --> 34:42.819
You're already taking on the
big issues way better than us.

34:42.863 --> 34:44.691
- No pressure.

34:44.734 --> 34:47.172
Yeah, no pressure.

34:47.215 --> 34:50.305
So for now, your only job
is to do the exercises,

34:50.349 --> 34:54.222
and I promise you,
the fear will subside.

34:54.266 --> 34:56.398
You will feel safe again.

34:56.442 --> 34:58.705
We all will.

35:16.201 --> 35:18.942
